Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.76,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.14,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:29.89,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
