Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.13,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Wow, really?}Vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.00,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Okay, girl. Have faith in yourself!}Mình phải tự tin lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Trust that it's all going to go right.}Nhất định mọi chuyện sẽ suôn sẻ.
