Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:38.48,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{Deep breath in... Deep breath out.\NDeep breath in... Deep breath out.}Thở sâu... Hít vào... thở ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.06,Default,CF Staff,0,0,0,,{Kessoku Band! You're up soon!}Nhóm Kessoku! Hãy chuẩn bị!
