Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.88,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay! Wanna do a huddle?}Rồi! Làm vòng tròn tình bạn nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.20,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Oh! Or that thing where we put \Nour hands together and go "Yeah!"}À, trò đặt tay vào nhau xong lên tinh thần á?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.42,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I love it! Let's do it!}Hay đó! Làm thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.58,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{So stuffy.}Phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Left hands, all!}Tay trái nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.35,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Just do it already!}Làm thôi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.43,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You too, Gotoh-san!}Gotoh nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.80,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right.}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.83,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Now, let's play hard and have fun!}Nào, hãy cùng cố hết sức nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{One, two...}Hai, ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.72,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Yê!
