Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.72,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Big Sis!}Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.50,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Give it your best!}Cố lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.89,Default,Fan 1/2,0,0,0,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{M-My fans!}Fan của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.18,DefaultTop,Fan 1/2,0,0,0,,{Give it your best!}Cố lên nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{People from my class, too...}Bạn cùng lớp nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's not just what I expected!}Không như mình nghĩ!
