Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.95,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Gimme a good show, 'kay?!}Diễn cho cháy vào đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.29,Default,Shuka Mob H,0,0,0,,{Reeks of booze!}Hôi quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.96,Default,Shuka Mob K,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure she should be here...}Sao lại có người nguy hiểm như vậy ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.45,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Huh? Whu?}Ủa? Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.25,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Don't ignore me, Bocchi-chan!}Đừng bơ chị chứ, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.76,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{It's me, Big Sister Kikuri!}Chị Kikuri nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I shouldn't have invited her!}Mình không nên mời chị ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.43,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Get it together, loser!}Đủ rồi đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.80,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai... Uncle, uncle!}C-Chị... cổ em...
