Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:40.40,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{We're Kessoku Band, and we \Nmainly play outside of school.}Bọn mình là nhóm Kessoku, thường hay chơi bên ngoài trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:47.66,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{We hope our performance helps make\Ntoday more memorable for everyone.}Hi vọng buổi diễn hôm nay sẽ khiến mọi người nhớ đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:53.41,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{And if you're interested, we hope \Nyou'll come to see us at our club!}Nếu có hứng thú hãy đến nghe tại club nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.94,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Here comes our first song...}Bài hát đầu tiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:03.42,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{as Kessoku Band!}Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.99,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:11.30,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with being young?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.14,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{Hey, why doesn't it stop?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.31,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{The rhythm that I can't stop}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.99,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{keeps reverberating through my body}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.19,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{The melody playing in my earphones}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:34.99,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{is the only thing that lets me be who I am}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.20,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{The sky is tinged in red}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:45.00,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{But what color is my soul?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.40,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{Tell me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:50.99,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{where should I go?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.98,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{I've always been searching}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.20,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{for something precious (hey!)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:02.82,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{If everything's going to be lost some day}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:06.09,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{let's engrave it as deep as we can (now!)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.50,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{My most pathetic nights \Nand cackling laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:13.68,Songs_ED3,ED,0,0,0,,{And days when I couldn't say \Nmore than "You know..."}
